name: Average Joe
text: Food was good, buffet is always full! They are always busy when I come in which is good, the wait staff ensures that my visit is pleasant and my drink is always full.

name: Ryan H
text: Food is good but the last few times I have been in there most of the tables are dirty and sticky. Makes me wonder about the kitchen.

name: Mary Wright
text: Salad bar was empty. Three of us had no salad with our meal. Never refilled it. Very dirty tables and kitchen floor and counters. Never again!
